他在说什么? 什么啊
Wh-what's happening ?

737
00:58:35,920 --> 00:58:36,990
我也不知道 爸...
I don't know, daddy.

738
00:58:37,020 --> 00:58:38,830
它要跑掉啦
Oh, it's getting away !

739
00:58:39,130 --> 00:58:42,920
克里顿 不要 你这样会吓到她
No ! You'll only frighten her more.

740
00:58:48,940 --> 00:58:52,900
喔! 好主意 真是好主意
Oh, yes. Absolutely, my dear. Good idea.

741
00:58:52,940 --> 00:58:53,910
你们在干什么啊!
What are you doing ?

742
00:58:53,940 --> 00:58:54,940
不怕把它们全吓跑了...
Do you want to frighten them off?

743
00:58:54,980 --> 00:58:57,910
起来 起...
Get up ! Get...

744
00:58:57,950 --> 00:59:01,900
千万别起来
Don't get up.

745
00:59:02,950 --> 00:59:06,910
嗯?
Ah.

746
00:59:29,980 --> 00:59:31,950
你好
Hello.

747
00:59:34,980 --> 00:59:36,950
哈哈...
Ooh.

748
00:59:36,980 --> 00:59:40,940
我也很高兴能认识你!
It's very nice to meet you too.

749
00:59:41,990 --> 00:59:45,950
哈哈...皇后陛下 你真会开玩笑
Oh, your majesty, you're such a tease.

750
00:59:49,000 --> 00:59:51,970
你好 你好 我是阿基米德布教授
Hello. Hello. Uh, archimedes Q. Porter at your service.

751
00:59:52,000 --> 00:59:53,970
喔! 你的手真有力呀
Aah ! Quite a grip you've got.

752
00:59:54,000 --> 00:59:56,970
喔 谢谢
Oh, thank you.

753
00:59:57,000 --> 00:59:59,970
这是给我的呀
Is that one of mine ?

754
01:00:00,010 --> 01:00:02,980
哈哈 喔 真舒服呀 克里顿先生
Oh, this is wonderful, mr. Clayton !

755
01:00:03,010 --> 01:00:03,980
你看呀 他们这是在认识新朋友
Look ! Look ! Social grooming.

756
01:00:04,010 --> 01:00:07,970
那就恭喜你了 教授
Congratulations, professor.

757
01:00:08,020 --> 01:00:11,970
我们的梦想成真了
Our dream has come true.

758
01:00:13,020 --> 01:00:16,980
你干什么你 不要碰我
Give me that ! Hey, what're you doing ?

759
01:00:17,020 --> 01:00:19,990
干什么 你怎么... 嘿 还给我 还我...
Stop that ! Stop ! Hold on, now ! Leave that !

760
01:00:20,030 --> 01:00:22,000
这不是开玩笑 不是闹着玩的
That is not to be played with !

761
01:00:37,040 --> 01:00:40,010
- 教我好吗? - 说猩猩话
- Can you teach me ? - Speak gorilla ?

762
01:00:40,050 --> 01:00:44,010
嗯 对
Mmm, yes.

763
01:01:04,070 --> 01:01:07,040
哈哈 我说了什么呀
Good heavens ! What did I say ?

764
01:01:07,070 --> 01:01:10,040
珍妮留下陪泰山
That jane stays with tarzan.

765
