留下? 可是我们不是已经...
Stay ? But I thought we'd already...

766
01:01:13,080 --> 01:01:16,050
泰山...我...
But, tarzan, i, i... Whoa!

767
01:01:21,090 --> 01:01:25,050
- 那不是我的衣服吗? - 喔 完了...
- Is that my dress ? - Oh, no.

768
01:01:28,100 --> 01:01:31,060
喔...爸
Oh, daddy. - Ooo-ooo.

769
01:01:31,100 --> 01:01:35,060
把它...还给我
Give it to me!

770
01:01:38,110 --> 01:01:42,060
不
No !

771
01:01:57,120 --> 01:02:00,090
走
Go !

772
01:02:00,130 --> 01:02:03,100
- 等等 泰山 - 快走
- Wait ! Wait ! Tarzan ! - Go now !

773
01:02:03,130 --> 01:02:07,090
珍妮快走啊 快呀
Jane, quickly ! Hurry ! Come along.

774
01:02:26,150 --> 01:02:28,120
哥查 我不是...
Kerchak, I didn't...

775
01:02:28,160 --> 01:02:32,110
对不起...我... - 我要求你 保护我们的家族
I'm sorry, I-I asked you to protect our family,

776
01:02:33,160 --> 01:02:37,120
而你出卖了我们
And you betrayed us all.

777
01:03:05,190 --> 01:03:08,160
我真的搞不懂
I'm so confused.

778
01:03:08,200 --> 01:03:11,160
跟我来
Come with me.

779
01:03:11,200 --> 01:03:15,160
有个地方我早该带你去了
There's something I should've shown you long ago.

780
01:04:34,280 --> 01:04:38,240
这是我吗
Is this me ?

781
01:04:40,290 --> 01:04:44,250
那他是我爸爸...还有...
And this is my father, and,

782
01:04:44,290 --> 01:04:47,260
我的...
And my...

783
01:04:47,290 --> 01:04:50,260
你现在都知道了
Now you know.

784
01:04:50,300 --> 01:04:54,260
泰山 不管你是怎么决定
Tarzan, I just want you to be happy,

785
01:04:54,300 --> 01:04:58,260
我都希望你快乐
Whatever you decide.

786
01:05:44,350 --> 01:05:46,320
不管我在哪里
No matter where I go

787
01:05:46,350 --> 01:05:49,360
你永远都是我的妈妈
You will always be my mother.

788
01:05:53,360 --> 01:05:57,320
你也永远在我心里面
And you will always be in my heart.

789
01:06:14,380 --> 01:06:18,340
再见泰山
Oh, good-bye, tarzan.

790
01:06:18,390 --> 01:06:21,380
泰山 哈哈...你来啦
Tarzan ! I'm so glad you found us in time.

791
01:06:21,420 --> 01:06:24,380
我真高兴你赶上 来 快上船吧!
Let's get in the boat, shall we ?

792
01:06:25,390 --> 01:06:29,390
我们走 请上船吧
Mustn't keep the captain waiting.

793
01:06:31,400 --> 01:06:34,370
泰山
Tarzan !

794
01:06:34,400 --> 01:06:37,370
喔 我们晚了一步 都是你啦
We're too late ! I can't believe it !

795
01:06:37,400 --> 01:06:39,370
叫你先问好怎么走就不会耽误时间了
If you'd have pulled over and asked for directions...

796
