我们来不及说再见
We didn't get to say good-bye.

797
01:06:42,410 --> 01:06:45,380
对呀 反正眼不见心不烦! 谁需要你 你走呀
Yeah, well, good riddance ! All right ? Who needs ya ? Huh ?

798
01:06:45,410 --> 01:06:48,420
