Yes, darwin and kipling. Queen victoria.

809
01:07:20,450 --> 01:07:22,420
我没有见过她 可是听说她人很好喔
I haven't met her, but I heard she's awfully nice.

810
01:07:22,450 --> 01:07:26,410
- 珍妮 跟我在一起? - 嗯
- And i'll be with jane ? - Mmm. Mmm.

811
01:07:26,450 --> 01:07:30,410
是呀...在一起 哈哈...
Yes, with jane.

812
01:07:30,460 --> 01:07:34,420
喔...好滑...
Ooh ! Slippery.

813
01:07:54,480 --> 01:07:57,450
泰山
Tarzan !

814
01:07:57,480 --> 01:07:59,450
抓住他
Get him !

815
01:07:59,490 --> 01:08:03,450
别让他跑了
Get him !

816
01:08:03,490 --> 01:08:07,450
- 泰山 - 珍妮
- Tarzan! - jane !

817
01:08:27,510 --> 01:08:29,480
这里又怎么了
What's going on here ?

818
01:08:29,520 --> 01:08:31,520
克里顿 克里顿 救我
Clayton. Clayton, help.

819
01:08:31,550 --> 01:08:35,480
我们认识吗
Have we met ?

820
01:08:38,530 --> 01:08:40,490
喔 对啦...
Ah, yes.

821
01:08:40,530 --> 01:08:42,500
那个人猿
The ape man.

822
01:08:42,530 --> 01:08:46,490
克里顿...你 你...
Clayton, you... You...

823
01:08:48,540 --> 01:08:50,500
喔 真是抱歉对你招待不周喔
So sorry about the rude welcome, old boy.

824
01:08:50,540 --> 01:08:53,510
可是我装你那些猩猩朋友进笼子的时候
But I couldn't have you making a scene...

825
01:08:53,540 --> 01:08:56,510
可容不得你闹事啊
When we put your furry friends in their cages.

826
01:08:56,540 --> 01:09:00,500
- 为什么 - 为什么?
- Why ? - Why ?

827
01:09:00,550 --> 01:09:03,520
还不是为了大把的钞票
For 300 pounds sterling a head.

828
01:09:03,550 --> 01:09:06,520
