Actually, I have you to thank, my boy.

829
01:09:06,550 --> 01:09:10,510
没有你我做不成生意
Couldn't have done it without you.

830
01:09:11,560 --> 01:09:15,520
把他跟其他人关在一起
Lock him up with the others.

831
01:09:17,560 --> 01:09:20,530
咦! 听起来像是泰山在叫
Uh, that sounded like tarzan.

832
01:09:20,570 --> 01:09:22,540
他好像...有麻烦啦...
He sounded like, like he was in trouble.

833
01:09:22,570 --> 01:09:26,530
谁理他 叫他的新朋友去救他呀 我才不管呢...
Yeah, well, why doesn't he get his new friends to help him ? I don't care.

834
01:09:26,570 --> 01:09:29,540
啊...我听够了
That's it !

835
01:09:29,580 --> 01:09:33,540
啊...我实在受不了你这个阴阳怪气的脾气
I've had it with you and your emotional constipation !

836
01:09:33,580 --> 01:09:36,550
泰山需要我们帮忙 我们就去帮他
Tarzan needs us, and we're gonna help him !

837
01:09:36,580 --> 01:09:40,540
听懂了吗? 你给我安静坐好 手抓牢啦
You got that ? Now, pipe down and hang on tight.

838
01:09:40,590 --> 01:09:42,560
我们要上船了
We've got a boat to catch.

839
01:09:51,600 --> 01:09:54,570
啊...我从来没这么开心过
I've never felt so alive !

840
01:09:54,600 --> 01:09:57,570
很好 我就快要杀你啦
Good ! 'Cause i'm gonna kill ya !

841
01:09:57,600 --> 01:10:01,560
我现在没时间跟你玩
No time for that now, missy.

842
