泰山 没有用的 不要...
Tarzan, it's no use. Don't !

843
01:10:29,640 --> 01:10:33,600
- 克里顿 - 没错 克里顿
- Clayton. - Yes, clayton.

844
01:10:33,640 --> 01:10:35,610
是克里顿欺骗我们
Clayton betrayed us all.

845
01:10:35,640 --> 01:10:39,600
- 我很抱歉 泰山 - 不...
- I'm so sorry, tarzan. - No.

846
01:10:39,650 --> 01:10:43,610
是我的错 我出卖我的家族
I did this. I betrayed my family.

847
01:10:43,650 --> 01:10:45,620
哥查说的对
Kerchak was right.

848
01:10:45,650 --> 01:10:49,610
