我马上就放你出来
I'm going to have you out of this in a second.

868
01:14:10,860 --> 01:14:14,820
这个太有用了
Right. This should do the trick.

869
01:14:36,880 --> 01:14:38,850
躲猫猫 嗯
Hiding, are we ?

870
01:14:38,890 --> 01:14:40,850
- 太好了 - 克里顿 你...
- Go on ! - Clayton, you...

871
