你是属于我们家族的一份子
That you have always been one of us.

883
01:17:18,040 --> 01:17:22,000
现在起这个家族就要交给你了
Our family will look to you now.

884
01:17:23,050 --> 01:17:25,020
不 哥查
No, kerchak.

885
01:17:25,050 --> 01:17:29,010
照顾他们
Take care of them,

886
01:17:29,060 --> 01:17:33,010
我儿
My son.

887
01:17:39,070 --> 01:17:43,020
保护他们
Take care of them.

888
01:19:02,150 --> 01:19:06,110
跟这里比 伦敦实在太小了
London will seem so small compared to all this.

889
01:19:07,150 --> 01:19:09,120
我会想你 珍妮!
I will miss you, jane.

890
01:19:09,160 --> 01:19:13,110
- 布小姐 - 我知道了 好 马上来
- Miss porter! - I, I know. I'm coming.

891
01:19:13,160 --> 01:19:17,120
嗯...我应该跟你说再见了
Well, I suppose we should say good-bye.

892
01:19:29,180 --> 01:19:32,140
再见
Good-bye.

893
01:19:41,190 --> 01:19:45,150
再见 泰山 再见
Good-bye, tarzan ! Good-bye.

894
01:19:45,190 --> 01:19:49,150
哦! 我一定会想念那孩子
Oh, i'm going to miss that boy.

895
01:19:57,200 --> 01:20:01,160
珍妮 我觉得你应该留下来
Jane, dear, I can't help feeling that you should stay.

896
01:20:02,210 --> 01:20:04,210
爸别再讲了 我们讲好的
Daddy, please don't. We've been through all of this.

897
01:20:04,250 --> 01:20:07,210
我...我怎么可能留下 我...
I couldn't possibly st...

898
01:20:07,250 --> 01:20:08,180
我属于英国
I, I belong in england with you,

899
01:20:08,210 --> 01:20:12,210
跟着你 还有那个社会...
With people, and... Aah !

900
01:20:15,220 --> 01:20:19,180
可是你爱他
But you love him.

901
01:20:22,230 --> 01:20:26,190
去吧...
Go on.

902
01:20:51,260 --> 01:20:55,220
