Thank you. Thanks for getting my glove.

903
01:20:55,260 --> 01:20:59,220
谢谢...
Thank you.

904
01:21:06,270 --> 01:21:10,230
我...
Well...

905
01:21:12,280 --> 01:21:16,240
我怎么老糊涂了呢 嗯! 哎! 船长
But, what... What am I doing ? Captain ?

906
01:21:16,280 --> 01:21:18,250
告诉他们 你根本就没找到我们
Tell them that you never found us. Eh ?

907
01:21:18,280 --> 01:21:22,240
反正每天都有人在森林里失踪嘛
After all, people get lost in the jungle every day. Right ?

